strings:
<voice_0x01000EF4><se_def>Prince Charmles: I say, <leader>!
Show me what it is you've got there!

<voice_0x01000EF5><se_def>Prince Charmles: Well, well... A salamango, eh?
The Chancellor said that Argon lizards absolutely adore these.

<voice_0x01000EF6><se_def>Prince Charmles: A sleeping lizard will wake up at the
slightest whiff of one, apparently!
I suppose that's proof enough!
